{% comment %}
  Sección visual: cómo medir + tips (guía de tallas PDP)
{% endcomment %}

<div class="tallas-extra">
  <section class="tallas-howto" aria-labelledby="tallas-howto-title">
    <h3 class="tallas-howto__title" id="tallas-howto-title">
      <span class="tallas-howto__icon" aria-hidden="true">📏</span>
      Cómo tomar tus medidas
    </h3>

    <div class="tallas-howto__layout">
      <div class="tallas-howto__steps">
        <article class="tallas-step">
          <div class="tallas-step__row">
            <span class="tallas-step__badge tallas-step__badge--a">A</span>
            <div class="tallas-step__copy">
              <strong class="tallas-step__label">Pecho</strong>
              <p>Mide alrededor de la parte más ancha del pecho, justo debajo de las axilas. Mantén la cinta métrica horizontal.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tallas-step__mini" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M14 8 L8 16 L11 18 L11 48 L37 48 L37 18 L40 16 L34 8 Q24 4 14 8Z" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.25)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)"/>
              <line x1="11" y1="24" x2="37" y2="24" stroke="#ffd700" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
              <circle cx="40" cy="24" r="7" fill="#ffd700"/><text x="40" y="27" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="8" font-weight="700">A</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tallas-step">
          <div class="tallas-step__row">
            <span class="tallas-step__badge tallas-step__badge--b">B</span>
            <div class="tallas-step__copy">
              <strong class="tallas-step__label">Largo</strong>
              <p>Mide desde el punto más alto del hombro (junto al cuello) hasta la parte inferior de la camiseta.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tallas-step__mini" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M14 8 L8 16 L11 18 L11 48 L37 48 L37 18 L40 16 L34 8 Q24 4 14 8Z" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.25)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)"/>
              <line x1="24" y1="12" x2="24" y2="48" stroke="#00c851" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
              <circle cx="36" cy="30" r="7" fill="#00c851"/><text x="36" y="33" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="8" font-weight="700">B</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tallas-step">
          <div class="tallas-step__row">
            <span class="tallas-step__badge tallas-step__badge--c">C</span>
            <div class="tallas-step__copy">
              <strong class="tallas-step__label">Altura</strong>
              <p>Recomendamos elegir tu talla según tu altura.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tallas-step__mini" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <ellipse cx="20" cy="8" rx="6" ry="7" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.25)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)"/>
              <line x1="20" y1="15" x2="20" y2="58" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="28" y1="10" x2="28" y2="58" stroke="#c9a0ff" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
              <circle cx="34" cy="34" r="7" fill="#c9a0ff"/><text x="34" y="37" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="8" font-weight="700">C</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="tallas-howto__visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="tallas-jersey-pair">
          <svg class="tallas-jersey-svg" viewBox="0 0 120 140" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M28 18 L14 38 L22 42 L22 118 L98 118 L98 42 L106 38 L92 18 Q60 10 28 18Z" fill="rgba(0,200,81,0.12)" stroke="rgba(0,200,81,0.55)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M28 18 Q42 30 60 30 Q78 30 92 18" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <line x1="22" y1="58" x2="98" y2="58" stroke="#ffd700" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="5 3"/>
            <line x1="60" y1="28" x2="60" y2="118" stroke="#00c851" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="5 3"/>
            <circle cx="104" cy="58" r="10" fill="#ffd700"/><text x="104" y="62" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="11" font-weight="700">A</text>
            <circle cx="104" cy="88" r="10" fill="#00c851"/><text x="104" y="92" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="11" font-weight="700">B</text>
          </svg>
          <svg class="tallas-jersey-svg" viewBox="0 0 120 140" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M28 18 L14 38 L22 42 L22 118 L98 118 L98 42 L106 38 L92 18 Q60 10 28 18Z" fill="rgba(255,215,0,0.08)" stroke="rgba(255,215,0,0.45)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="72" y1="20" x2="72" y2="130" stroke="#c9a0ff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="5 3"/>
            <circle cx="88" cy="72" r="10" fill="#c9a0ff"/><text x="88" y="76" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="11" font-weight="700">C</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tallas-tips" aria-labelledby="tallas-tips-title">
    <h4 class="tallas-tips__title" id="tallas-tips-title">
      <span aria-hidden="true">💡</span> Tips
    </h4>
    <div class="tallas-tips__grid">
      <div class="tallas-tip">
        <span class="tallas-tip__icon" aria-hidden="true">📐</span>
        <p>Usa una cinta métrica y mide sobre tu cuerpo, no sobre otra prenda.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tallas-tip">
        <span class="tallas-tip__icon" aria-hidden="true">👕</span>
        <p>Para un ajuste cómodo, elige tu talla según tu medida de pecho.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tallas-tip">
        <span class="tallas-tip__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚽</span>
        <p>Si estás entre dos tallas, elige la mayor para más comodidad.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="tallas-footnote">
    <span aria-hidden="true">ⓘ</span>
    Medidas aproximadas en centímetros.
  </p>
</div>
